	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />What style of music are you trying to make?<br /><br />One thing that I find that brings about creativity is to set limits onto yourself. And lucky for you, the 2A03 is severely limited. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_lol.gif" alt=":lol:" title="Laughing" /><br /><br />Speaking of which, what kind of music engine are you using? Famitone? Will you be utilizing all four (or five) channels?<br /><br />For what it's worth, I think my compositions (or whatever you call them) improved significantly after I did several classical/baroque NSF covers. So borrowing from classical music might help.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


